<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>USDT Withdrawal Request Submitted - DiTokens CRM</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .info-message {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .receipt {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .receipt-header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .receipt-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .receipt-row.total {
            border-top: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .receipt-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .receipt-value {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .total .receipt-value {
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            background-color: #ff6b35;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üí∏ USDT Withdrawal Request</h1>
            <p>Your withdrawal request has been submitted</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="info-message">
                <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
                <p>Your USDT withdrawal request has been successfully submitted and is now under review by our team.</p>
                <div class="status-badge">PENDING REVIEW</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="receipt">
                <div class="receipt-header">
                    <h3>üìÑ Withdrawal Request Details</h3>
                    <p style="color: #6c757d; margin: 0;">Request ID: {{withdrawalId}}</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Request Date:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{requestDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Withdrawal Amount:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{amount}} USDT</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Network:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{network}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Destination Wallet:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{walletAddress}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Processing Fee:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{processingFee}} USDT</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row total">
                    <span class="receipt-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="receipt-value">{{totalAmount}} USDT</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h4>‚è∞ Processing Information:</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Review Time:</strong> Withdrawal requests are typically reviewed within 24-48 hours</li>
                    <li><strong>Business Hours:</strong> Processing occurs during business days (Monday-Friday)</li>
                    <li><strong>Status Updates:</strong> You'll receive email notifications when your request status changes</li>
                    <li><strong>Verification:</strong> We may require additional verification for security purposes</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üí° What happens next?</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Our team will review your withdrawal request</li>
                    <li>We'll verify your wallet address and account details</li>
                    <li>Once approved, USDT will be sent to your specified wallet</li>
                    <li>You'll receive a confirmation email when processed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/wallets/usdt-withdraw" class="cta-button">View Withdrawal Status ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team at support@ditokens.com or visit our help center.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2024 DiTokens CRM. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #bdc3c7;">
                This email confirms your USDT withdrawal request. Please keep it for your records.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
